div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/msj1665703016984.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/msj1665703016984.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"msj1665703016984\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $web\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"msj1665703016984___web_300839\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return an indication of whether the current application was started by the Web Request Dispatcher (WRD) or Uniface Anywhere.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"msj1665703016984__topic_d91526e1_d91527e1_d91528e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"msj1665703016984__p_d91529e1_d91530e1_d91531e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$web</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"msj1665703016984__section_w1582ab1b7b5_w1583ab1b7_w1584ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"msj1665703016984__p_d91532e1_d91533e1_d91534e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">if ($web=\"\")</code> ...</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"msj1665703016984__topic_d60937e1_d60938e1_d60939e1_d60940e1_d60941e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d999882e75\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"msj1665703016984__table_d10130e1_d10131e1_d10132e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$web</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"msj1665703016984__table_d10130e1_d10131e1_d10132e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"msj1665703016984__table_d10130e1_d10131e1_d10132e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"msj1665703016984__table_d10130e1_d10131e1_d10132e1__entry__1\">\n JTI\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"msj1665703016984__table_d10130e1_d10131e1_d10132e1__entry__2\">The application was activated by Uniface\n                        Anywhere. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"msj1665703016984__table_d10130e1_d10131e1_d10132e1__entry__1\">\n URD\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"msj1665703016984__table_d10130e1_d10131e1_d10132e1__entry__2\">The application was activated by the WRD. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"msj1665703016984__table_d10130e1_d10131e1_d10132e1__entry__1\">\n ERR\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"msj1665703016984__table_d10130e1_d10131e1_d10132e1__entry__2\">Error determining the context. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"msj1665703016984__table_d10130e1_d10131e1_d10132e1__entry__1\">\n \"\"\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"msj1665703016984__table_d10130e1_d10131e1_d10132e1__entry__2\">The application was not activated by the WRD. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"msj1665703016984__topic_d60942e1_d60943e1_d60944e1_d60945e1_d60946e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d999882e148\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"msj1665703016984__d7121e20\">Use in Dynamic and Static Server Page components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"msj1665703016984__topic_d60947e1_d60948e1_d60949e1_d60950e1_d60951e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d999882e158\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"msj1665703016984__p_d91547e1_d91548e1_d91549e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$web</span> function returns a string that indicates whether the current application was started by the WRD or by Uniface Anywhere. This allows you to provide conditional processing depending on whether a component is running in a web browser, Uniface Anywhere, or a normal application.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gna1665702540285.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>webgen</a><p>Generate an XHTML document from the layout definition and the component definition of a static server page.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hbu1719365402351.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>webget</a><p>Load data from a client request into a static server page (USP), reconnect to the database if applicable, set a current occurrence, and activate a detail or error trigger, if required.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530055\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530055\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$web Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $web Return an indication of whether the current application was started by the Web Request Dispatcher (WRD) or Uniface Anywhere. $web Example: if ($web=\"\") ... Return Values Table 1. Values returned by $web Value Meaning JTI The application was activated by Uniface Anywhere. URD The application was activated by the WRD. ERR Error determining the context. \"\" The application was not activated by the WRD. Use Use in Dynamic and Static Server Page components. Description The $web function returns a string that indicates whether the current application was started by the WRD or by Uniface Anywhere. This allows you to provide conditional processing depending on whether a component is running in a web browser, Uniface Anywhere, or a normal application. Related Links webgen Generate an XHTML document from the layout definition and the component definition of a static server page. webget Load data from a client request into a static server page (USP), reconnect to the database if applicable, set a current occurrence, and activate a detail or error trigger, if required. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}